{
  "stem": "3360.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Arnold was evidently a very ardent Hitler fan, admirer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She was actually in love with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She had a large picture of Hitler in the classroom, which was not required.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- excuse me-- she would bring fresh flowers every day, a small bouquet of violets or something every day to stick behind the frame for the Fuhrer.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so it goes without saying that you can imagine what this woman was made of and what her-- what her state of mind was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was unfortunate, extremely unfortunate, for me, because not every teacher in that school was anything like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "However, as I much later found out, the principle of that school wanted by all means to push out the Jewish students, the Jewish pupils and to 'purify it,' quote, unquote.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so I guess they used whatever means they could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It-- it was-- it was an over-ambitious scheme of his, because the government had required that by such and such year and such and such time this should occur.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But he was going to push it and make it happen sooner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that point in time, the regime had been in place well over a year, as I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by that point in time, they had already instituted a whole lot of anti-Semitic measures, laws enacted, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of the things that they required in every school is an hour of instruction on National Socialism.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, that's not what it was called.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I can't recall what it was called.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's what it basically was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so what happened was that when I started there and this class was taking place, and of course, the teacher was this woman-- although, we had other teachers.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
